Class LongMediator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.validator2.LongMediator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExtendedLongMediator

    public class LongMediator
extends java.lang.Object
    A long mediator is a mediator for a long with a name. A long mediator is not mutable.

    Silvan Wyss
